Package com.cafean.client.ui.swing.accordion

Interface AccordionSelectionModel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultAccordionSelectionModel
    public interface AccordionSelectionModel
    Implementations represent the current state of the selection and expansion in an Accordion component. Both are defined as a single index into the component's data model.
